<p class="wikiPara">
Now that RichFaces 4.0.0.Final is just a couple weeks away, we've had time to finalize our <a href="http://richfaces.org/showcase" target="" class="regularLink">RichFaces Showcase</a> and get it hosted up on Google App Engine (GAE)!  Now you have a great way to explore all of the great RichFaces 4.0 components, and give them a try yourself (<i class="wikiEmphasis">no login required</i>).  Plus we have all the <a href="http://community.jboss.org/wiki/HowtouseRichFaces40withGoogleAppEngine" target="" class="regularLink">instructions you need</a> to get your own application running up on GAE.  You can even host your own version of the RichFaces Showcase application!
</p>

